♪ I KNOW WHAT COMFORT IS ♪

38:18.291 --> 38:21.458
♪ AND I CAN'T SEE
WHY I SHOULD ♪

38:21.458 --> 38:26.792
♪ BUT I COULD DO
MOST ANYTHING FOR YOU ♪

38:26.792 --> 38:29.125
♪ AND YOU KNOW I WOULD ♪

38:29.125 --> 38:31.583
♪ I TRY TOO HARD ♪

38:31.583 --> 38:35.542
♪ AND THEN I GIVE UP
WAY TOO EASILY ♪

38:35.542 --> 38:40.208
♪ I'M THE RUNNER-UP
INSIDE OF YOU ♪

38:40.208 --> 38:42.500
♪ AND YOU'RE THE WINNER
INSIDE OF ME ♪

38:44.166 --> 38:47.208
♪ LOSE YOUR WAY ♪

38:48.166 --> 38:52.125
♪ AND I WILL FOLLOW ♪

38:52.125 --> 38:53.417
♪ HERE TODAY ♪

38:56.166 --> 38:59.333
♪ AND HERE TOMORROW ♪

38:59.333 --> 39:03.667
♪ BUT MY FREEDOM, I KNOW ♪

39:03.667 --> 39:09.542
♪ I'LL NEVER LET YOU GO ♪

39:13.125 --> 39:16.208
♪ I STILL WISH
ON THE EVENIN' STAR ♪

39:16.208 --> 39:20.166
♪ AND I SUPPOSE
I ALWAYS WILL ♪

39:20.166 --> 39:23.291
♪ EVERY CHILD
LOSES SOMETHIN' ♪

39:23.291 --> 39:26.333
♪ A WHOLE LIFE
CAN'T FULFILL ♪

39:27.625 --> 39:30.250
♪ AND WHEN YOU CRY,
I FEEL THE SKY ♪

39:30.250 --> 39:33.625
♪ BURST OPEN IN MY VEINS ♪

39:33.625 --> 39:36.750
♪ IF LOVIN' YOU
MAKES A SLAVE OF ME ♪

39:36.750 --> 39:39.792
♪ THEN I'LL SPEND
MY WHOLE LIFE IN CHAINS ♪

39:39.792 --> 39:42.375
I JUST, UM...

39:42.375 --> 39:44.542
I HOPE WHEREVER SHE IS,
SHE'S HAPPY.

39:48.041 --> 39:51.000
SHE'S HAPPY.

39:52.458 --> 39:55.417
SHE'S LOOKING DOWN
ON YOU...

39:56.208 --> 39:57.667
AND SHE'S
VERY HAPPY.

40:00.208 --> 40:03.083
♪ I'LL NEVER LET YOU GO ♪

40:03.083 --> 40:06.417
♪ WALK THE LINE ♪

40:07.875 --> 40:11.125
♪ I'LL WALK INSIDE YOU ♪

40:11.125 --> 40:12.917
♪ CHANGE YOUR MIND ♪

40:15.208 --> 40:18.542
♪ LET YOUR LOVE DECIDE YOU ♪

40:18.542 --> 40:22.291
♪ IT'S THE REASON I KNOW ♪

40:22.291 --> 40:24.333
♪ YOU'LL NEVER LET ME GO ♪

40:24.333 --> 40:25.875
GRAMS?

40:25.875 --> 40:28.458
HOW COULD YOU,
JENNIFER?

40:31.417 --> 40:35.750
YOU PACKED UP
ALL MY STUFF.

40:35.750 --> 40:37.625
I WENT TO THAT
FUNERAL TODAY

40:37.625 --> 40:39.667
TO TRY TO GIVE YOU
SOME SUPPORT

40:39.667 --> 40:42.083
AND TO TRY
TO RECTIFY
SOME OF THE DAMAGE

40:42.083 --> 40:43.917
IN OUR FRAGILE
RELATIONSHIP,

40:43.917 --> 40:45.375
ONLY TO FIND YOU
HEARTLESSLY

40:45.375 --> 40:46.959
THUMBING YOUR NOSE
AT ME,

40:46.959 --> 40:48.917
IN A HOUSE OF GOD,
NO LESS.

40:48.917 --> 40:51.125
GRAMS, THAT SPEECH
WASN'T FOR YOU.

40:51.125 --> 40:51.667
THAT WAS FOR ABBY.

40:54.083 --> 40:56.417
AND I REGRET IT.

40:56.417 --> 40:58.458
I DO.

40:58.458 --> 41:00.625
AND--AND I KNOW
THAT IT WAS WRONG,

41:00.625 --> 41:04.125
AND--AND I'M SORRY
THAT I OFFENDED
YOUR BELIEFS--

41:04.125 --> 41:05.625
THIS IS NOT ABOUT
MY BELIEFS

41:05.625 --> 41:07.083
OR FREE SPEECH
OR ANY OTHER

41:07.083 --> 41:08.417
PHILOSOPHICAL
NONSENSE.

41:08.417 --> 41:10.333
THIS IS ABOUT
THE TRUTH,

41:10.333 --> 41:12.125
AND THE TRUTH
IS YOU DELIBERATELY
TRIED TO WOUND ME

41:12.125 --> 41:14.208
IN THAT CHAPEL.

41:14.208 --> 41:15.458
YOU DECIDED
TO TAKE OUT

41:15.458 --> 41:18.291
ALL YOUR
PAIN AND RAGE
AT THE WORLD ON ME.

41:18.291 --> 41:19.291
WAIT, GRAMS--

41:19.291 --> 41:20.708
YOU WANT UNDERSTANDING?

41:20.708 --> 41:21.792
HOW ABOUT A LITTLE
UNDERSTANDING IN RETURN?

41:21.792 --> 41:24.625
HOW ABOUT A LITTLE
COMPASSION FOR ME?

41:24.625 --> 41:26.792
NOT JUST FOR MY BELIEFS,
BUT FOR ME,

41:26.792 --> 41:28.166
YOUR GRANDMOTHER,
WHO LOVES YOU,

41:28.166 --> 41:29.125
WHO WOULD DO ANYTHING
FOR YOU,

41:29.125 --> 41:30.291
WHO WOULD DIE FOR YOU.

41:30.291 --> 41:33.333
WAIT, GRAM--GRANDMA,
WAIT A MINUTE.
JUST LISTEN.

41:33.333 --> 41:34.792
YOU SHOULD BE LIVING
WITH SOMEONE ELSE,

41:34.792 --> 41:38.750
SOMEONE YOU RESPECT,
AND CLEARLY, I AM NOT
THAT PERSON.

41:38.750 --> 41:41.500
ALL THE TIME YOU WASTE
REBELLING AGAINST ME

41:41.500 --> 41:43.500
IS GETTING YOU NOWHERE,

41:43.500 --> 41:45.500
SO WHILE IT PAINS ME

41:45.500 --> 41:47.667
MORE THAN YOU WILL
EVER KNOW, JENNIFER,

41:47.667 --> 41:49.708
I WANT YOU TO MOVE OUT.

41:50.667 --> 41:52.708
FIND SOMEWHERE ELSE
TO LIVE.

